Luo Cha secara sengaja?

24
00:03:32,970 --> 00:03:34,290
Awak sangat bijak.

25
00:03:34,770 --> 00:03:35,970
Tak kira betapa bijaknya awak,

26
00:03:36,690 --> 00:03:38,490
