akan mati dibunuh budak suruhan
yang berpangkat paling rendah

28
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:43,930
seperti saya di Istana Chao Sheng.

29
00:03:47,890 --> 00:03:48,650
Lembing Tai Chang?

30
00:03:52,930 --> 00:03:53,850
Apa yang awak buat terhadap Bai Jue?

31
00:03:54,210 --> 00:03:55,210
Syurga dan bumi dan jadi sejuk,

32
00:03:55,730 --> 00:03:57,450
tak mungkin Bai Jue masih hidup.

33
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:14,820
Kuasa iblis?

34
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,580
Atas arahan Iblis Agung,

35
00:04:25,020 --> 00:04:26,260
Putera Jing Jian,
sila tinggalkan tempat ini

36
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:27,540
agar dapat lindungi sendiri.

37
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:28,860
Betari phoenix?

38
00:04:29,940 --> 00:04:30,780
Dewa Ibu?

39
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:32,460
