kuasa iblis yang begitu kuat?

40
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:33,980
Pasti ia dikurniakan Dewa Ibu saya.

41
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:35,940
Dewa Ibu saya

42
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:38,980
