81
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:23,470
Awak Ketulan Ais jahat.

82
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:25,230
Segala-gala yang awak lakukan
sejak sedar,

83
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:26,470
