dapat menggembirakan orang.

84
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:28,350
Sangat sakit ini!

85
00:07:29,710 --> 00:07:32,190
Kini, perbuatan jenayah Wu Huan
dah terdedah.

86
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:33,710
Selepas bunuh dia,

87
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:35,790
