131
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:27,190
Ini bulu phoenix.

132
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:30,550
Orang tua hantar pesanan kepada saya
melaluinya setiap kali untuk cari saya.

133
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:31,590
Saya balik dulu.

134
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:33,990
Cik.

135
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,770
