136
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:39,340
♪Hati awak selamanya♪

137
00:10:40,530 --> 00:10:43,490
♪Mencarikan awak♪

138
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,680
♪Beribu-ribu batu♪

139
00:10:46,770 --> 00:10:47,770
Patutlah.

140
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:50,370
Awak selalu muncul di sisi saya

141
