142
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:30,710
Tanpa Zhi Yang,

143
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:34,310
berdasarkan kamu bertiga,
dapat halang sayakah?

144
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:35,990
Zhi Yang tak berada di sini. Habis?

145
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:54,190
Kalau saya tak cedera parah
dan kuasa dewa tak terjejas

146
00:13:54,190 --> 00:13:56,230
semasa saya sedar,

147
00:13:56,430 --> 00:13:57,630
saya takkan biar awak
hidup sampai sekarang.

148
00:13:58,230 --> 00:13:58,710
Wu Huan.

149
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,310
Apa maksud kebaikan?

150
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:00,990
Apa maksud kejahatan?

151
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:02,510
