155
00:14:10,470 --> 00:14:11,590
kehidupan semula awak

156
00:14:12,870 --> 00:14:14,670
pasti berkaitan dengan malapetaka itu.

157
00:14:18,230 --> 00:14:18,910
Bai Jue,

158
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:20,710
awak membuat rancangan dengan teliti.

159
00:14:21,710 --> 00:14:23,350
Awak sangka perbuatan awak

160
00:14:24,350 --> 00:14:26,150
