paling kecil kepada dia?

161
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:27,670
Diam!

162
00:14:32,190 --> 00:14:33,630
Apabila hal sebenar diketahui,

163
00:14:34,190 --> 00:14:35,230
perbuatan awak

164
00:14:35,230 --> 00:14:36,950
mesti ganggu dan menyeksa dia

165
00:14:36,950 --> 00:14:37,510
