169
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,230
Apa yang dia cakap?

170
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,630
Bara Raja Burung?

171
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,470
Feng Ran ditimpa masalah?

172
00:15:26,590 --> 00:15:27,910
Dewa Agung Shang Gu,
saya merayu kepada awak.

173
00:15:28,190 --> 00:15:29,070
