Cuma harap...

201
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:31,030
Cuma harap awak selamatkan anak saya.

202
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:33,310
Selamatkan dia.

203
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:38,990
Jian'er.

204
